Interface Dictionary

All Superinterfaces:
Map<String,Object>
All Known Implementing Classes:
DataAsset, JSONDataFile, JSONDictonary
public interface Dictionary extends Map<String,Object>
Map-like interface that provides methods for retrieving the values as values of specific Java types.
